✗ Generic constraint solving algorithms (e.g., Z3, CVC5 mechanics)
✗ Standard PID or Fuzzy Logic mathematical theories

================================================================================
WHAT IS ACTUALLY PROTECTED
================================================================================

✓ The architecture of replacing "Execution Loops" with "Logic Solvers" for control
✓ The specific method of using "UNSAT" as a safety mechanism in control loops
✓ The "Deadbeat" and "Stiction" logic patterns implemented via temporal logic
✓ The integration of a SAT/SMT solver directly into a real-time feedback loop
✓ The specific Tau specifications developed for physical state governance

